<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    
    <link href="css/switchery.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="css/demo.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="css/easydropdown.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="css/global.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="javascript/switchery.js"></script>
    <script src="javascript/jquery-3.1.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="javascript/jquery.easydropdown.js"></script>
    <title></title>
    <style type="text/css">
        .switchery{
            float:right;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background:#fff;">

    <div class="menu">
        <div>分店POS控制台</div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="index.html">运行状况</a></li>
            <li><a href="reg1.html">服务注册</a></li>
            <li class="active"><a href="pos.html">POS配置</a></li>
            <li>快捷按键</li>
            <li>系统日志</li>
            <li>软件更新</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
        <header>
            <a>退出登录</a>
            <a>重启服务</a>
        </header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="item">
                <div class="item-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li class="row">
                            <span class="text-title">收银金额零头处理</span>
                            <span class="text-content">（对最终的应收金额，零头处理方式）</span>
                            <!--<select>
                                <option class="option-new" style="height:30px;">抹零到角</option>
                                <option class="option-new">抹零到角</option>
                                <option class="option-new">抹零到角</option>
                            </select>-->

                            <select class="dropdown" tabindex="9" data-settings='{"wrapperClass":"flat"}' style="float:right;">
                                <option value="1">抹零到角</option>
                                <option value="2">抹零到角</option>
                                <option value="3">抹零到角</option>
                                <option value="4">抹零到角</option>
                                <option value="5">抹零到角</option>
                            </select>



                        </li>
                        <li class="row">
                            <span class="text-title">收银保留结算窗口</span>
                            <span class="text-content">（完成收银后，是否保留最后的结算窗口）</span>
                            <input type="checkbox" class="js-switch01" style="right:0;" checked />
                        </li>
                        <li class="row">
                            <span class="text-title">收银小票模板设置</span>
                            <span class="text-content">（小票纸有58mm和88mm两种宽度，根据小票机类型做相应选择）</span>
                            <select class="dropdown" tabindex="9" data-settings='{"wrapperClass":"flat"}' style="float:right;">
                                <option value="1">58mm</option>
                                <option value="2">58mm</option>
                                <option value="3">58mm</option>
                                <option value="4">58mm</option>
                                <option value="5">58mm</option>
                            </select>
                            <div class="form-group" style="margin-right:30px;float:right;margin-top:-7px;">
                                <input type="button" class="btn-little" value="模板编辑" />
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="row">
                            <span class="text-title">促销定时更新周期</span>
                            <span class="text-content">（指默认情况下总部设定促销后多长时间更新到分店同步）</span>
                            <select class="dropdown" tabindex="9" data-settings='{"wrapperClass":"flat"}' style="float:right;">
                                <option value="1">4小时</option>
                                <option value="2">4小时</option>
                                <option value="3">4小时</option>
                                <option value="4">4小时</option>
                                <option value="5">4小时</option>
                            </select>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="btn-item">
                    <input type="button" class="btn btn-save" value="保存" style="margin-left:30px;" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        var _height = window.screen.height - 255;
        $('.item').css('height', _height + 'px');


        //开关控件
        var elem = document.querySelector('.js-switch01');
        var init = new Switchery(elem);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
